{"tid":1631360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"留意到以緊急法打緊急法幾work","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:18.000Z","uid":34457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"05512e4cdd60e2d5972685af39ce8ebc17cf8772","tid":1631360,"uid":34457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"政府要即刻出黎澄清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d841eefc466983cfeb627a69a2970ae717055c","tid":1631360,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aae929f73c5ee0c08be3b5f2e1ed2f0a38f96665","tid":1631360,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"7cf79556fa1499b759bc2138ff2caba8a1d2ab69","tid":1631360,"uid":34457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fb80cc29c3932e66f579c694c5997d68a94837d","tid":1631360,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8e4a50e29271ce7d53e490b30bc3bc9040dd0eb","tid":1631360,"uid":175668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"絕對係 引起公眾恐慌"},{"pid":"e38ee79c1c303ebebf21a8130599c0002e3f466b","tid":1631360,"uid":203251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:38.000Z","msg":"即係點"},{"pid":"8feb4f8ef206bb671f0a7c49b9bc0df3ef8e0067","tid":1631360,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快拎錢"},{"pid":"7cc4059e19c0773288bca9cb7b383f4ebda320cc","tid":1631360,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:25:19.000Z","msg":"因為緊急法，可能大量僱主犯法？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全民罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164779bf1be53f805405f83346a899d93c1083f9","tid":1631360,"uid":271420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:25:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6d6559bed65fafc3365c92833abf88c5a45863a6","tid":1631360,"uid":34457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:18.000Z","msg":"再推推"}]}